title: Dead Men Don't Count (Western, 1968) Spaghetti Western film directed by Rafael Romero

sources.title: Dead Men Don't Count (Western, 1968) Spaghetti Western film directed by Rafael Romero
sources.description:
Damon and Steffen are paired up bounty hunters falsely accused of murder in a lawless town ruled by racketeering lawmen.

Original title: ¿Quién grita venganza? (1968) AKA:  Dead Men Don't Count, (I morti non si contano), Cry for Revenge

Director: Rafael Romero Marchent
Writers: Marco Leto, Vittorio Salerno

Main Cast:
Anthony Steffen as Fred Dannon
Mark Damon as Johnny Dannon
María Martín as Witwe Reed/Mrs. Rogers
Dyanik Zurakowska as Elizabeth
Luis Induni as Steve Rogers
Piero Lulli as Sheriff Bob Watson
Raf Baldassarre as Greg Lassiter
Barta Barri as Forrest
Josè Marco as Jack Logan
Jesús Guzmán as Jonathan Alegría
Miguel del Castillo as Judge Wright
Raf Baldasarre as Gregory Lassiter
Carlos Romero Marchent as Forrest Jr.


0:00 Full Spaghetti Western Movie
07:32 Fred and Johnny arrive in Blackston to investigate mysterious deaths.
18:45 The mysterious stranger claims to be Jaguar while confronting the Sampson gang.
21:34 Sheriff Rodgers threatens the bounty hunters to leave Blackston immediately.
32:16 Fred discovers Sheriff Thompson's secret connection to the railroad company.
35:47 Elizabeth Forrest shares the devastating story of her murdered family.
45:53 Johnny confronts the Lassiter gang at the saloon over stolen land deeds.
48:23 Johnny discovers a mysterious inscription inside the gold-plated revolver.
59:24 Elizabeth reveals her father's murder was orchestrated by corrupt officials.
1:15:40 Fred and Johnny exposes the corrupt land scheme, & face the Lassiter brothers in a dramatic final showdown.
